src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點睇都係泫雅大食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:45:43.000Z","msg":"屌,岩岩SEARCH過下<br />\n好似真係一齊過<br />\n咁無啦無啦<br />\n肯定廿次以上<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1718955/org/cf3356d729fb830924a633967158851b.jpg/C2fad--WSAnyGGuiOknxoNUXh-ttbN7WnD3qmpw96po?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1718955%2Forg%2Fcf3356d729fb830924a633967158851b.jpg%2FC2fad--WSAnyGGuiOknxoNUXh-ttbN7WnD3qmpw96po%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=2adc8c14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n粉絲提到張賢勝上傳該照片的日期是2016年6月30日，而泫雅最近就承認自己和E'Dawn於2016年5月開始交往。對比兩個時間，張賢勝的失戀文在泫雅和E'Dawn拍拖後一個月上傳，的確有一點微妙。雖然沒有証據顯示，張賢勝的文章與泫雅有關，但不少粉絲都紛紛評論「兩年後才看懂」。另一方面E'Dawn出道後就因為外型與張賢勝相似，所以有「張賢勝2.0」的花名，難免會令這段關係變得更受關注。不論張賢勝和泫雅曾經交往與否，以及當中是否存在小三，相信偶像大方認愛亦只是希望得到粉絲的認同和祝福。"},{"pid":"84c3a3c45a130dec6653fadf2f4c51d2181ae89b","tid":1312841,"uid":138138,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:51:25.000Z","msg":"吊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />岩岩諗到樣野唔知關唔關事<br />\n張賢勝入左伍個LOOK 陽光左有肌肉唔再係道友樣<br />\n唔係張賢勝2.0 係咪因為咁又抄鳩佢先練肌肉呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/03/20190315_EN_ZHANG_8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F03%2F20190315_EN_ZHANG_8.jpg&h=8589cb88&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/03/20190315_EN_ZHANG_9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F03%2F20190315_EN_ZHANG_9.jpg&h=4923cb16&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6943294